data.description: Gorgeous one detached family house.  First floor has huge living room with hardwood floors thought out the house, formal dining room, kitchen includes a stove, refrigerator, microwave. Access to the backyard.  Second floor has two huge bedrooms, with a full bathroom. Basement is big, open space with a utility area. Driveway for five cars, garage and big yard. Excellent neighborhood, great school district, shops, LIRR busses, and much more.
